00:22:16,044 --> 00:22:17,462
EVERYONE'S WORRIED ABOUT YOU

359
00:22:17,545 --> 00:22:20,923
<i>Oh yeah, I haven't eaten anything.</i>

360
00:22:23,968 --> 00:22:25,219
